fredr
  • Reference

Return a FRED series as an xts object.

Given a series ID, return observations of that series as an xts object.

fredr_series(series_id, ...)

Arguments

series_id

A string ID for the FRED series. Use fredr_search to find the series_id of a series.
...

A series of named parameters to be used in the query. Must be of the form param_key = "param_value". Acceptable parameters are endpoint-specific. See fredr_endpoints for a list of endpoints and fredr_docs access to the endpoint web documentation.

Value

An xts object with observation dates in the index corresponding to parsed numeric observations as values.

Examples

fredr_series(
  series_id = "UNRATE",
  observation_start = "1980-01-01",
  observation_end = "2000-01-01",
  unit = "chg"
)
